    "description": "RoboJep is a Platforming/Physics Based Puzzle Game. Fly through obstacles, solve small puzzles and avoid dangerous obstacles!<br><br>Progress through 15 levels and at the end, you will be fighting the Narrator!<br><br><br>  【Features】<br><br>                                    【<strong>Take advantage of the Physics Flight System!</strong>】<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/38c66596b2ad67b42c5b65839ee49874.poster.avif?t=1756402427\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/38c66596b2ad67b42c5b65839ee49874.webm?t=1756402427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/38c66596b2ad67b42c5b65839ee49874.mp4?t=1756402427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>                                    【<strong>Traverse dangerous obstacles! Some of them are moving :)</strong> 】<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/5a84c43265a1bedd85adf8d0e6f42521.poster.avif?t=1756402427\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/5a84c43265a1bedd85adf8d0e6f42521.webm?t=1756402427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/5a84c43265a1bedd85adf8d0e6f42521.mp4?t=1756402427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>                                   【<strong>Carry objects to their destination to unlock locations!</strong>】<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/313718e943876419c9a47198a614780e.poster.avif?t=1756402427\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/313718e943876419c9a47198a614780e.webm?t=1756402427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/313718e943876419c9a47198a614780e.mp4?t=1756402427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>                                   【<strong>Your gonna be dying a lot :)</strong>】<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/9e2bdce697e851c6159ceeba3b3b8d26.poster.avif?t=1756402427\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/9e2bdce697e851c6159ceeba3b3b8d26.webm?t=1756402427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/9e2bdce697e851c6159ceeba3b3b8d26.mp4?t=1756402427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>                                   【<strong>And finally meet the Narrator!</strong>】<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/780eeb7f47f2687f534699643b2a6e5c.poster.avif?t=1756402427\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/780eeb7f47f2687f534699643b2a6e5c.webm?t=1756402427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715580/extras/780eeb7f47f2687f534699643b2a6e5c.mp4?t=1756402427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
